      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait sorry i didnt realize i had to change stations. i thought the lner left from paddington? if i have to go to kings cross what is the best way to do that part, like is there a specific tube line i should look for or should i just grab a taxi? also are there usually a lot of delays on those tube lines that would mess up my timing?",
